.I val (lsl) 
: 
.B int -> int -> int
.sp

.B n lsl m
shifts 
.B n
to the left by 
.B m
bits\&.
The result is unspecified if 
.B m < 0
or 
.B m >= bitsize
,
where 
.B bitsize
is 
.B 32
on a 32\-bit platform and
.B 64
